%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20121218%2F51189997&h=ee59f6fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20121218/51189997</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有Hard Feeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」(其實係施老板響電視講咖...有片為證 <a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/webapps/program_video/index.php?video_id=12142897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fwebapps%2Fprogram_video%2Findex.php%3Fvideo_id%3D12142897&d=VT7FvYTkX2N6WbAcYSLOrIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=bccf136c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fwebapps%2Fprogram_video%2Findex.php%3Fvideo_id%3D12142897&h=6672519d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/webapps/program_video/index.php?video_id=12142897</a>  )<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"18d51c85abdada42665138bd064de3fcf06da780","tid":477591,"uid":53441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T02:36:21.000Z","msg":"都就快聖誕節啦"},{"pid":"8f81cf0385930adf4ee927cec531af15c55894ce","tid":477591,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老屎忽最鐘意鬥食屎<br />\n<br />\n食開2舊屎就話人食一舊就喊哂咁口做乜野,再搏人讚佢好醒好勁<br />\n<br />\n依D垃圾文化幾時先可以清除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地個年代努力小小都已經發到圍啦<br />\n佢地食一舊屎可以上位 我地食十舊屎當食飯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又係到解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我話比你聽成功從來都冇易話<br />\n以前同而家都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有你呢種思想既人永遠都唔會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係果句<br />\n你考試由零分考到50分易d,定由90分